The paper discusses the application of XCS, a classifier system, in reinforcement learning tasks, which falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The discussion of multi-step environments and sequential decision problems suggests a connection to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
